                "key": "Tutorial",
                "string_values": [
                  "<p>An elite Fatui special agent who can manipulate Anemo in battle. In combat, they will use the Hunt Down skill to attach a Life Bond to characters they hit. While Life Bond is active, the character will take continuous DMG, and Hunt Down will deal more DMG to them.</p>"
